                        15:00 HRS.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Bot√≥n Ubicaci√≥n con MANO -->
                <div class="relative">
                    <a
                        href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/JEZujShzKuuvdKmH7"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="bg-[#4E5F49] hover:bg-[#3d4a39]
                    text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded text-sm md:text-base
